nodes.text: "Episode I Easter Eggs" is an article in Star Wars Insider 48 written by Mark Cotta Vaz. It features various easter eggs found in Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace and debunks other easter eggs that some fans claimed they had seen. On the last page is a small article by Star Wars Insider editor Jon Bradley Snyder, "I Was an Episode I Easter Egg!," that tells of an Episode I easter egg of his own.
